{"tid":815434,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"讀港大咁勁仲要問屋企人拎零用錢？","createTime":"2018-09-12T05:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T07:52:44.000Z","uid":8556,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b74fa6a1b383377505b47539d7d490f0e58f360f","tid":815434,"uid":8556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/125924_98b2631b0d4222a58476b822d81c4a26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F125924_98b2631b0d4222a58476b822d81c4a26.png&h=21349f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n痴線成75%港大仔仲有問屋企拎錢，入得大學都成年人啦，係咪應該獨立啲為自己嘅洗費負責呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實有啲人衝出嚟話，人地有錢你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錯我係吹佢唔脹，但75%咁誇張，其他u肯定冇咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全想像唔到港大窮撚點生存，同人講要返part-time一定俾人笑到面黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入面啲窮撚港大仔仲要comment話自己好生性仲可以幫補家計，咁都拎得嚟打飛機，人地落club屌女你就走數返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇港大窮撚出嚟講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6756cc777fa17fb2d2e5bb676dd88794f445ea40","tid":815434,"uid":175598,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87821d009c1822c6000410c3d240ee7a51c3c0a4","tid":815434,"uid":8556,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"6756cc777fa17fb2d2e5bb676dd88794f445ea40","tid":815434,"uid":175598,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20